MySpotIsHot
===========

WiFi hotspot setup script for Ubuntu 12.10+

Start the script::
	
	$ ./Myspotishot.sh

If for some chance it is not executable::

	$ chmod u+x Myspotishot.sh

The script will guide you through the setup

Enjoy!

